PREFIX wdt: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/direct/>
PREFIX wd: <http://www.wikidata.org/entity/>
SELECT ?politician ?spouse WHERE {
  ?politician wdt:P106 wd:Q82955 ; wdt:P26 ?spouse .
  ?spouse wdt:P27 wd:Q183 .
}
LIMIT 10

PREFIX wdt: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/direct/>
PREFIX wd: <http://www.wikidata.org/entity/>
SELECT ?daughter ?spouse WHERE {
  wd:Q25310 wdt:P40 ?daughter .
  ?daughter wdt:P21 wd:Q6581072 .
  ?daughter wdt:P26 ?spouse .
}

PREFIX wdt: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/direct/>
PREFIX wd: <http://www.wikidata.org/entity/>
ASK WHERE {
  wd:Q128160 wdt:P585 ?cubanMissileCrisisDate .
  wd:Q191721 wdt:P585 ?bayOfPigsInvasionDate .
  FILTER ( ?cubanMissileCrisisDate > ?bayOfPigsInvasionDate )
}

PREFIX wdt: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/direct/>
PREFIX wd: <http://www.wikidata.org/entity/>
PREFIX rdfs: <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#>
SELECT ?country ?countryLabel ( COUNT( DISTINCT ?language ) AS ?languageCount ) WHERE {
  ?country wdt:P37 ?language .
  ?country wdt:P31 wd:Q6256 .
  OPTIONAL {
    ?country rdfs:label ?countryLabel .
    FILTER ( LANG( ?countryLabel ) = 'en' )
  }
}
GROUP BY ?country ?countryLabel
HAVING ( COUNT( DISTINCT ?language ) > 2 )
ORDER BY DESC ( ?languageCount )

PREFIX wdt: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/direct/>
PREFIX wd: <http://www.wikidata.org/entity/>
SELECT ?mountain ?height WHERE {
  ?mountain wdt:P31 wd:Q8502 ; wdt:P2044 ?height .
  FILTER ( ?mountain != wd:Q159621 )
}
ORDER BY DESC ( ?height )
LIMIT 1

PREFIX wdt: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/direct/>
PREFIX wd: <http://www.wikidata.org/entity/>
SELECT ?country ( COUNT( ?cave ) AS ?caveCount ) WHERE {
  ?cave wdt:P31 wd:Q35509 .
  ?cave wdt:P17 ?country .
}
GROUP BY ?country
HAVING ( COUNT( ?cave ) > 10 )

PREFIX pq: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/qualifier/>
PREFIX p: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/>
PREFIX ps: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/statement/>
PREFIX wd: <http://www.wikidata.org/entity/>
SELECT ?statement ?date WHERE {
  wd:Q211 p:P463 ?statement .
  ?statement ps:P463 wd:Q458 .
  ?statement pq:P580 ?date
}
